function Timeline(){ return(

  • (25% sold)

    The First Bite

    10% of proceeds from minted Donuts are donated to a charitable cause chosen by existing holders.

  • (50% sold)

    Half Way

    An additional 10% of proceeds from minted Donuts are donated. 20 Donuts are randomly airdropped to existing holders.

  • (75% sold)

    Almost Gone

    Exclusive IRL merch released for Donut holders (limited run).

  • (100% sold)

    All Gone

    An additional 10% of proceeds from minted Donuts are donated. Holders will be able to participate in the artistic direction of a new NFT

) } export default Timeline;
